GADSDEN COUNTY TIMES and continuing THE CHATTAHOOCHEE TRIBUNE Published each Thursday at 15 S Madison Street A lOHN H PERRI NEWSPAPER ESTABLISHED 1901 Quincy Florida Entered in th pot ottic at Quincy Florida undei th Act ot March ft 1879 a matter of the eecond clasv One Year 300 Two Years 550 Six Months 175 J L Hufhinwii PuMulur national editorial as c 5 t l3 w Truman On Recession Former President Harry S Truman speaking out on the Current recession has offered some interesting advice In the first place Truman says that the recession we are now encountering is not proof that anything is seriously wrong with our economy Mr Truman believes that we are experiencing a lapse of confidence on the part of the people of the United States con fidence in what we are doing and the economic policies being pursued by the Administration Assuming that Mr Truman is not nonpartisan since he has never been and making allowances for that he is still entitled to his opinion on the economic state of the Union On several counts we think he offers good advice Among other things that Mr Truman recommends is less emphasis on"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-01-27T17:02:17.065Z", "group": ["ndnp/fu", "university-of-florida-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn95047334/1958-03-06/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_immokalee_ver01:data:sn95047334:00529042474:1958030601:0130/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=303&w=208", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_immokalee_ver01:data:sn95047334:00529042474:1958030601:0130/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=607&w=416", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/fu/batch_fu_immokalee_ver01/data/sn95047334/00529042474/1958030601/0130.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["quincy", "florida", "united states", "gadsden", "gadsden county"], "location_city"